{"text_id":129440,"tokens":["The"," belief"," that"," clear"," urine"," is"," a"," sign"," of"," proper"," hydration"," comes"," from"," the"," understanding"," that"," water"," dil","utes"," substances"," in"," the"," body","."," When"," you","'","re"," well","-","hydrated",","," your"," body"," has"," plenty"," of"," water"," to"," expel"," waste"," products",","," which"," can"," make"," your"," urine"," appear"," lighter"," or"," clear","."," Urine"," is"," a"," waste"," product"," that"," contains"," the"," substances"," your"," body"," doesn","'","t"," need",","," including"," excess"," water","."," The"," kidneys"," filter"," these"," substances"," out"," of"," the"," bloodstream"," and"," ex","crete"," them"," in"," urine","."," The"," color"," of"," urine"," can"," be"," influenced"," by"," the"," concentration"," of"," these"," waste"," products","."," When"," you","'","re"," well","-","hydrated",","," your"," body"," has"," an"," excess"," of"," water",","," and"," your"," urine"," may"," be"," very"," light"," or"," clear"," because"," it","'","s"," diluted","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," if"," you","'","re"," dehydrated",","," your"," body"," doesn","'","t"," have"," enough"," water"," to"," dilute"," these"," waste"," products",","," so"," your"," urine"," can"," appear"," darker","."," This"," is"," why"," many"," people"," believe"," that"," if"," your"," urine"," isn","'","t"," clear",","," you"," aren","'","t"," drinking"," enough"," water","."," However",","," it","'","s"," important"," to"," note"," that"," while"," urine"," color"," can"," be"," a"," general"," indicator"," of"," hydration",","," it","'","s"," not"," a"," definitive"," measure","."," Many"," factors"," can"," affect"," urine"," color",","," including"," certain"," foods",","," medications",","," and"," medical"," conditions","."," For"," example",","," eating"," beets"," can"," turn"," your"," urine"," pink"," or"," red",","," certain"," medications"," can"," turn"," it